---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import PageHeader from "@/components/PageHeader.astro";
---
<Base title="Terms of Service" description="The terms governing use of the Splatter Impacts storefront.">
  <PageHeader title="Terms of Service" lead="The basic terms for using this store and buying our products." />
  <section class="container-page max-w-3xl py-12 space-y-6 text-steel-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <p>This is a template terms-of-service document for the Splatter Impacts storefront and should be reviewed by the store owner and, ideally, legal counsel before launch.</p>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-steel-50">Eligibility & lawful use</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">You must be of legal age to purchase shooting-sports products in your jurisdiction. You are responsible for ensuring that ownership and use of any product you purchase is legal where you live and where you use it.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-steel-50">Assumption of risk</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">Shooting sports are inherently dangerous. By purchasing and using our products you accept all risk of injury or damage and agree to follow all applicable safety rules and laws. See our Range Safety page for general guidance.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-steel-50">Products & pricing</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">We strive for accuracy in product descriptions, images, and prices, but errors can occur. We reserve the right to correct errors and to cancel orders affected by them.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-steel-50">Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">To the fullest extent permitted by law, Splatter Impacts is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or misuse of our products.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
